<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>World Cup Competition 2026</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>🏆 World Cup Competition 2026</h1>
  <p>Pick 6 teams. Rank them. Follow the live leaderboard.</p>
</header>

<section class="card">
  <h2>🏅 Live Leaderboard</h2>
  <div id="leaderboard">Loading...</div>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <details>
    <summary>📜 Competition Rules</summary>

    <h3>How to Enter</h3>
    <p>
      Send Martin your 6 team selections ranked 1st through 6th and pay the €10 entry fee.
      Entries close Thursday 11th June at 8PM Irish time.
    </p>

    <h3>How Teams Earn Points</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Win = 4 pts</li>
      <li>Draw = 2 pts</li>
      <li>Goal scored = 1 pt</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Ranking Multipliers</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>1st Pick ×6</li>
      <li>2nd Pick ×5</li>
      <li>3rd Pick ×4</li>
      <li>4th Pick ×3</li>
      <li>5th Pick ×2</li>
      <li>6th Pick ×1</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Penalty Shoot-outs</h3>
    <p>
      Shoot-out goals do not count. The winning team still receives
      4 points for the win.
    </p>

  </details>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>🌍 Team Scores</h2>
  <div id="teams">Loading...</div>
</section>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
